quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,121,"Tuma nde dawno…óaa ka …ďeynguure maa…óa, hi…óa werna muumini en tommbor…óe hare. Alla ko Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  3,122,"Tuma nde feddeeji …ói…ói e mo'on himmu no, nde cooyoton, ko Alla non woni Gi…óo ma…ď…ďe. Ko Alla woni ko gom…óim…ďe …ďen haani hoolorde"
  3,123,"Gom…óii Alla Wallii on √Īalnde Badri, tawi ko on hoy…ďe. Hulee Alla, belajo'o on yettay [Mo]"
  3,124,"Nde maakanayno…óaa gom…óim…ďe …ďen: \"Enee, yonaŇčtaa on nde Joomi mo'on …ďeydanta on Malaa'ikaa…ďe guluuje tato jippinaa…ďe"
  3,125,"Pellet, si on mu√Ī√Īike on gom…óii, e arday on hawjere ma…ď…ďe, …óum …óoo, Joomi mo'on no ∆Āeydira on guluuje jowi Malaa'ika maandinaa…ďe"
  3,126,"Alla Wa…óiraali …óum si wanaa wewlere wonannde on, e no …ďer…óe mon …óen …óee∆īira …óum. Ballal iwrataa si wanaa ka Alla, On Foolu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  3,127,"Ko fii yo O Ta∆īu fedde e …ďen yeddu…ďe maa O Wirta …ďe, …ďe ruttoo ko …ďe sooyu…ďe"
  3,128,"Laatanaaki ma e fiyaake on hay e huunde : maa O Ja…ďan …ďe tuubuubuyee, maa O Leptu …ďe, pellet, kam…ďe ko …ďe too√Īoo…ďe"
  3,129,"Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Himo Haforana on mo O Muuyi, O Lepta on mo O Muuyi. Alla ko Haforoowo Yurmetee…óo"